The paper presents a collection of knowledge graphs that contain both numerical features and links to images for all entities, as well as entity alignments between pairs of KGs. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), computer vision (cs.CV), and natural language processing (cs.CL), as these fields often deal with multi-modal data and knowledge representation.
